n%20typically%20given%20to%20medications%20that%20carry%20the%20risk%20of%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBamboo%20Health%2C%20the%20company%20running%20Louisiana's%20prescription%20monitoring%20database%2C%20is%20ready%20to%20track%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcvs-walgreens-to-sell-abortion-pills-contested-by-scotus-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrugs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20March%2C%20Louisiana%20clinicians%20are%20required%20to%20log%20every%20mifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%20prescription%20they%20write%20in%20Bamboo's%20database%2C%20according%20to%20the%20New%20Orleans%20Health%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20Bamboo%20employee%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Bamboo%20announced%20its%20intention%20to%20monitor%20the%20drugs%20in%20an%20internal%20Slack%20channel%20last%20year%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20the%20company's%20legal%20obligation%20as%20Louisiana's%20prescription-monitoring%20vendor.%20The%20employee%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20sensitive%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%2C%20Indiana%2C%20and%20Idaho%20are%20considering%20similar%20measures%20for%20tracking%20these%20drugs.%20All%20three%20states%20work%20with%20Bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBamboo%20Health%20CEO%20Jeff%20Smith%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company's%20prescription%20monitoring%20platform%20must%20comply%20with%20state%20regulations.%20%26quot%3BThey%20determine%20how%20that%20data%20is%20managed%20and%20accessed.%20That's%20how%20it%20gets%20treated%20in%20Louisiana%20and%20anywhere%20else%20it%20would%20occur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMisoprostol%20isn't%20just%20for%20abortions.%20It's%20also%20used%20to%20treat%20stomach%20ulcers%2C%20manage%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fmiscarriage-rates-by-week%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emiscarriages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20stop%20excessive%20bleeding%20after%20c