liber%2C%20we%20will%20still%20do%20our%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20air%20defense%20unit%20commander%2C%20whose%20name%20is%20also%20Oleksiy%2C%20said%20Ukrainian%20lives%20depend%20on%20US%20military%20support.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20this%20issue%20will%20be%20resolved%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20on%20our%20own%20land%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20defend%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224649%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ukrainian%20serviceman%20fires%20a%20machine%20gun%20doing%20a%20training%20in%20the%20Kherson%20region%20in%20October%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cdd8d8b8b41a9673fa1bdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223099%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAir%20defense%20has%20been%20critical%20to%20Ukraine's%20fight%2C%20and%20there%20are%20serious%20concerns%20about%20how%20recent%20US%20decisions%20will%20affect%20these%20operations.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMarko%20Ivkov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20during%20a%20very%20heated%20Oval%20Office%20meeting%20in%20late%20February%20%E2%80%94%20which%20set%20the%20reduced%20US%20support%20in%20motion%20%E2%80%94%20that%20he%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20Ukraine%20was%20winning%20the%20war%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20uncertainty%20about%20what%20could%20happen%20without%20more%20US%20assistance.%20Some%20Ukrainian%20officials%20and%20lawmakers%20are%20hopeful%20that%20Ukraine%20can%20get%20by%20relying%20on%20its%20booming%20defense%20industry%20and%20support%20from%20European%20countries%2C%20but%20some%20of%20the%20American%20support%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzelenskyy-advisor-patriots-weapon-concern-over-trump-aid-cuts-ukraine-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especifically%20on%20air%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20is%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerhiy%20Rakhmanin%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Ukraine's%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20national%20security%2C%20defense%2C%20and%20intelligence%2C%20told%20BI%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcutting-satellite-imagery-weakens-ukraines-defenses-lawmaker-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkraine%20could%20manage%20without%3C%2Fa%3E%20American%20support%20for%20tactical%20operations%20at%20and%20near%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20but%20US%20involvement%20is%20crucial%20for%20more%20strategic%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20say%3B%20we'll%20see%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Svitlana%2C%20the%20only%20woman%20in%20the%20air%20defense%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20Ukrainians%20have%20put%20more%20weight%20on%20the%20US%20decision%20and%20warned%20that%20it%20could%20have%20serious%20consequences.%20Oleksandr%20Markushyn%2C%20a%20TDF%20commander%20and%20the%20mayor%20of%20Irpin%2C%20a%20city%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Kyiv%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20had%20been%20surprised%20by%20Trump's%20decisions%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20aftermath%20of%20a%20deadly%20Russian%20attack%20in%20Ukraine's%20Donetsk%20region%20on%20March%208.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cdd968585f1dff88b199a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223869%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExperts%20assess%20that%20without%20US%20assistance%2C%20Russia%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20Ukrainian%20vulnerability%20to%20further%20bombard%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Yan%20Dobronosov%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMarkushyn%2C%20speaking%20through%20a%20translator%20in%20a%20separate%20interview%20on%20Saturday%2C%20warned%20that%20if%20the%20US%20does%20not%20help%20Ukraine%2C%20then%20after%20it%2C%20Russia%20might%20move%20to%20take%20over%20other%20European%20countries.%20He%20led%20Ukraine's%20defense%20of%20Irpin%20during%20the%20early%20weeks%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20as%20Moscow's%20forces%20tried%20to%20take%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20is%20a%20powerful%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Markushyn%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20not%20the%20United%20States%2C%20no%20one%20will%20stop%20Russia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20on%20how%20they%20see%20recent%20decisions%20and%20the%20effects%20on%20Ukrainian%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20how%20long%20the%20pause%20in%20military%20aid%20could%20last.%20Trump%20has%20routinely%20suggested%20that%20he%20is%20not%20satisfied%20with%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy's%20approach%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzelenskyy-trump-clash-negotiations-deal-ukraine-russia-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20efforts%20to%20end%20Russia's%20grinding%20full-scale%20invasion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20just%20recently%20passed%20the%20three-year%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConflict%20analysts%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20a%20DC-based%20think%20tank%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-march-7-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia%20will%20likely%20take%20advantage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20pause%20in%20US%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20intensify%20its%20missile%20and%20drone%20attacks%20against%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy4lj15lyv3o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20weekend%20killed%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20people%2C%20wounding%20scores%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3C