5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20claimed%20that%20even%20India's%20B%20team%20can%20give%20Pakistan%20a%20run%20for%20their%20money.%20Gavaskar's%20remarks%20came%20after%20India%20beat%20Pakistan%20in%20a%20one-sided%20Champions%20Trophy%20encounter%20last%20month.%20He%20suggested%20that%20Pakistan%20can't%20even%20beat%20India's%20B%20team.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20B%20team%20(from%20India)%20certainly%20(can%20give%20Pakistan%20a%20run%20for%20their%20money).%20C%20team%2C%20I%20am%20not%20too%20sure.%20But%20a%20B%20team%20will%20be%20very%2C%20very%20hard%20to%20beat%20for%20Pakistan%20in%20their%20current%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gavaskar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Inzamam%20trashed%20Gavaskar's%20claim%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20latter%20once%20intentionally%20opted%20out%20of%20a%20match%20between%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20during%20his%20playing%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20won%20the%20match%2C%20they%20played%20well%20but%20Mr.%20Gavaskar%20should%20also%20take%20a%20look%20at%20stats.%20He%20once%20fled%20Sharjah%20to%20escape%20from%20playing%20against%20Pakistan.%20He%20is%20older%20than%20us%3B%20he%20is%20our%20senior.%20We%20greatly%20respect%20him%2C%20but%20you%20should%20not%20speak%20about%20a%20country%20like%20that.%20Sure%2C%20you%20have%20the%20right%20to%20praise%20your%20team%20as%20much%20as%20you%20want%2C%20but%20commenting%20like%20this%20on%20other%20teams%20is%20in%20bad%20taste%2C%26quot%3B%20Inzamam%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FCricketopiaCom%2Fstatus%2F1898716715800019047%2Fvideo%2F1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E24%20News%20HD%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhiel%20highlighting%20the%20all-time%20head-to-head%20stats%20between%20the%20two%20teams%2C%20Inzamam%20suggested%20that%20Gavaskar%20is%20ruining%20his%20legacy%20by%20making%20such%20controversial%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTell%20him%20to%20