Cp%3EMr%20Koshmr%20himself%20was%20stabbed%20three%20times%20-%20once%20in%20the%20head%2C%20once%20in%20the%20back%2C%20and%20once%20in%20the%20stomach.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20bleeding%20until%20the%20following%20night%20when%20we%20finally%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20vehicle%20to%20transport%20me%20to%20the%20hospital.%20My%20condition%20is%20stable%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20sense%20of%20safety%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20even%20know%20if%20my%20family%20and%20I%20will%20survive%20for%20much%20longer.%20Our%20names%20reveal%20our%20Alawite%20identity.%20Our%20dialect%20betrays%20us.%20Even%20our%20place%20of%20origin%20puts%20us%20at%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERenewed%20Violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20have%20flared%20between%20Alawites%20and%20Sunni%20militant%20factions%2C%20particularly%20Wahhabi-backed%20groups%20that%20have%20entered%20the%20region%20following%20Assad's%20ouster%20last%20year.%20These%20groups%20are%20not%20just%20targeting%20former%20Assad%20loyalists%20and%20ex-military%20personnel%20but%20also%20civilians%2C%20farmers%2C%20and%20religious%20minorities%2C%20including%20Christians%20and%20Shia%20Muslims.%20The%20violence%20escalated%20sharply%20following%20the%20killing%20of%20Sheikh%20Shaabaan%20Mansour%2C%20an%2086-year-old%20Alawite%20religious%20leader%2C%20and%20his%20son%20in%20Hama%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Footage%20have%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20where%20armed%20men%20are%20carrying%20out%20executions%20in%20public.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Footage%20have%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20where%20armed%20men%20are%20carrying%20out%20executions%20in%20public.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fglrp33eg_ndtv-exclusive-syria-_625x300_10_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootage%20have%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20where%20armed%20men%20are%20carrying%20out%20executions%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Syrian%20Observatory%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20at%20least%20973%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20March%206%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20in%20what%20it%20describes%20as%20%26quot%3Bethnic%20cleansing%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20civil%20war%20broke%20out%20in%202011%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Latakia%20and%20other%20Alawite-majority%20areas%20opened%20their%20homes%20to%20displaced%20Syrians%2C%20regardless%20of%20sect.%20We%20did%20it%20again%20in%202020%20and%202022.%20Syrian%20people%20don't%20discriminate%20-%20we%20are%20all%20Syrians.%20But%20the%20new%20government%20is%20failing%20to%20protect%20this%20unity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ibrahem%20Salamah%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20computer%20science%20engineer%20from%20Latakia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20week%2C%20a%20group%20of%20200%20fighters%2C%20led%20by%20former%20Assad%20army%20general%20Ghiath%20Dala%20and%20field%20commander%20Muqdad%20Fatiha%2C%20launched%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20forces%20of%20Abu%20Mohammad%20al-Julani%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20Hay'at%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%20and%20Syria's%20de%20facto%20ruler.%20The%20assault%20resulted%20in%20casualties%20among%20al-Julani's%20forces%2C%20prompting%20his%20government%20to%20mobilise%20reinforcements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20who%20joined%20al-Julani's%20forces%20from%20different%20Syrian%20provinces%2C%20and%20they%20are%20massacring%20the%20Alawites%2C%26quot%3B%2033-year-old%20Hussain%20Khalaf%20from%20Tartus%20told%20NDTV.%20The%20violence%20quickly%20spread%20to%20Jableh%2C%20Latakia%2C%20Banias%2C%20and%20its%20countryside%2C%20escalating%20into%20mass%20executions%2C%20home%20burnings%2C%20and%20forced%20displacements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEntire%20Families%20Massacred%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20foreign%20fighters%20from%20Chechnya%2C%20Uzbekistan%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20alongside%20Syrian%20factions%20known%20as%20al-Amshat%20and%20al-Hamzat%2C%20who%20are%20engaged%20in%20the%20fight.%20%26quot%3BThey%20killed%20entire%20families%20in%20Baniyas%2C%20Jableh%2C%20and%20Karto%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khalaf%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20have%20surfaced%20on%20Telegram%20and%20WhatsApp%2C%20showing%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20executions%20and%20massacres%20of%20entire%20families.%20In%20one%20particular%20video%2C%20a%20Syrian%20fighter%20was%20seen%20standing%20on%20top%20of%20bodies%20covered%20in%20blood.%20Another%20showed%20a%20man%20hanging%20from%20a%20crane%20in%20what%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20public%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20video%20urfaced%20online%20showed%20gun-weilding%20men%20standing%20on%20top%20of%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20family%20massacred.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22One%20video%20urfaced%20online%20showed%20gun-weilding%20men%20standing%20on%20top%20of%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20family%20massacred.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frddjfhpo_ndtv-exclusive-syria-_625x300_10_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20video%20urfaced%20online%20showed%20gun-weilding%20men%20standing%20on%20top%20of%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20family%20massacred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20uncle%20and%20aunt%20were%20driving%20from%20Damascus%20to%20Latakia%20when%20the%20violence%20erupted.%20Their%20son%2C%20my%20cousin%2C%20works%20in%20Dubai%20and%20has%20been%20trying%20desperately%20to%20contact%20them.%20They%20were%20forced%20to%20take%20refuge%20in%20the%20mountains%20near%20Al-Hwaiz%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Salamah%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Alawite%20religious%20leaders%20have%20called%20for%20peace%2C%20but%20fear%20is%20widespread.%20%26quot%3BDisplacement%20has%20already%20begun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BMany%20are%20heading%20into%20the%20mountains%2C%20but%20conditions%20there%20are%20brutal%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20cold.%20Others%20have%20sought%20refuge%20at%20the%20Hmeimim%20Airbase%2C%20which%20is%20controlled%20by%20Russia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBloodlines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Salamah%20comes%20from%20a%20mixed-religion%20family%20-%20his%20mother%20is%20Sunni%2C%20his%20father%20Alawite%2C%20and%20he%20has%20Christian%20relatives.%20He%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Alawites%20do%20not%20oppose%20the%20new%20Syrian%20government%20nor%20seek%20a%20return%20of%20Assad's%20rule.%20%26quot%3BWe%20suffered%20under%20Assad%2C%20just%20like%20all%20Syrians%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20attacks%2C%20however%2C%20suggest%20that%20elements%20within%20the%20new%20security%20forces%20remain%20unchecked.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20armed%20groups%20operating%20under%20the%20government's%20knowledge%20that%20still%20refuse%20to%20surrender%20their%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20videos%20being%20circulated%20online%20show%20bodies%20piled%20up%20after%20executions.%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Several%20videos%20being%20circulated%20online%20show%20bodies%20piled%20up%20after%20executions.%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fie4m33i_ndtv-exclusive-syria-_625x300_10_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20videos%20being%20circulated%20online%20show%20bodies%20piled%20up%20after%20executions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20flashpoints%20occurred%20in%20December%20when%20a%20video%20surfaced%20online%20showing%20the%20burning%20of%20Sheikh%20Abu%20Abdullah%20al-Hussein%20al-Khasibi's%20shrine%20in%20Aleppo.%20%26quot%3BArmed%20men%20stormed%20in%2C%20killed%20the%20shrine's%20guards%2C%20and%20set%20the%20place%20on%20fire.%20When%20Alawites%20protested%2C%20security%20forces%20opened%20fire%2C%20killing%20one%20person%20and%20injuring%20others%20in%20Homs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Salamah%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mr%20Koshmr%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20what%20is%20happening.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20ongoing%20sectarian%20cleansing%20campaign%20and%20a%20full-scale%20genocide%20targeting%20anyone%20identified%20as%20Alawite%20-%20whether%20by%20religion%2C%20dialect%2C%20or%20place%20of%20origin%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20rejected%20the%20idea%20that%20these%20killings%20are%20solely%20revenge%20for%20the%20Assad%20family.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Assad%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Syria's%20coastal%20region%20are%20among%20the%20poorest%20in%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20innocent%20civilians%20-%20engineers%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20farmers.%20Yet%2C%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20'hunting%20down%20Assad's%20remnants%2C'%20an%20entire%20sect%20is%20being%20massacred.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussian%20Blame%2C%20Indian%20Appeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khalaf%20believes%20Russia%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20recent%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20encouraged%20the%20remnants%20of%20the%20Assad%20regime%20to%20fight%20back%2C%20promising%20to%20protect%20the%20coast%20and%20Alawites%2C%20but%20then%20abandoned%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%20This%20left%20Al-Julani%20with%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20to%20commit%20massacres%20while%20Russia%20claimed%20to%20investigate%20the%20crimes%20to%20protect%20its%20geopolitical%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20create%20a%20financial%20donation%20campaign%20to%20help%20the%20victims.%20I%20ask%20for%20help%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20mounting%20reports%20of%20massac