ld%20market%20in%20Dubai%20is%20highly%20competitive%2C%20with%20numerous%20dealers%20offering%20attractive%20rates%20to%20entice%20buyers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20Dubai's%20gold%20markets%20have%20thrived%2C%20serving%20as%20significant%20centres%20for%20the%20collection%2C%20sale%2C%20and%20trade%20of%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20September%2025%2C%202024%2C%20the%20price%20of%2024K%20gold%20in%20Dubai%20was%20AED%20313.66%20per%20gram%20(approximately%20Rs%207%2C138.96%20per%20gram)%2C%20while%20in%20India%2C%20the%20price%20stood%20at%20Rs%208%2C225%20per%20gram%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bayut.com%2Fmybayut%2Fbuying-gold-in-dubai-vs-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBayut%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Gold%20Import%20Duties%20and%20Restrictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20manage%20the%20economic%20implications%20of%20gold%20imports%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20implemented%20various%20duties%20and%20regulations%20over%20the%20years.%20In%20July%202024%2C%20the%20customs%20duty%20on%20gold%20imports%20was%20reduced%20from%2015%20per%20cent%20to%20approximately%206%20per%20cent%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Findias-gold-duty-cut-likely-spark-buying-spree-during-festivals-2024-08-26%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20This%20reduction%20aimed%20to%20curb%20smuggling%20and%20boost%20legal%20imports%2C%20making%20gold%20more%20affordable%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20reduced%20duties%2C%20there%20are%20restrictions%20on%20the%20quantity%20of%20gold%20that%20can%20be%20imported%20into%20India%20without%20incurring%20additional%20taxes.%20Travellers%20must%20adhere%20to%20these%20guidelines%20to%20avoid%20legal%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20buying%20gold%20in%20Dubai%20may%20be%20cheaper%2C%20bringing%20it%20into%20India%20is%20subject%20to%20specific%20regulations%20and%20duties%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuty-Free%20Allowance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMale%20Passengers%3A%20Allowed%20to%20bring%20up%20to%2020%20grams%20of%20gold%2C%20valued%20at%20a%20maximum%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%2C%20without%20paying%20customs%20duty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFemale%20Passengers%3A%20Permitted%20up%20to%2040%20grams%20of%20gold%2C%20with%20a%20value%20limit%20of%20Rs%20100%2C000%2C%20duty-free.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECustoms%20Duty%20on%20Excess%20Quantity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuantities%20exceeding%20the%20duty-free%20allowance%20are%20subject%20to%20customs%20duties%2C%20which%20vary%20based%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20gold%20imported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reduction%20in%20import%20duties%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20surge%20in%20gold%20imports.%20In%20August%202024%2C%20India's%20gold%20imports%20reached%20a%20record%20%2410.06%20billion%2C%20driven%20by%20increased%20consumer%20demand%20ahead%20of%20the%20festive%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20surge%20in%20imports%20contributed%20to%20a%20widening%20trade%20deficit%2C%20which%20expanded%20to%20a%20ten-month%20high%20of%20%2429.65%20billion%20in%20the%20same%20month%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findias-august-merchandise-trade-deficit-widens-2965-bln-exports-fall-2024-09-17%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741585920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffrn3llc8_gold-generic_625x300_17_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgold-prices-in-dubai-vs-india-check-import-duty-restrictions-7889004%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kannada%20actress%20Ranya%20Rao's%20arrest%20at%20Benga