%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPremises%20linked%20to%20close%20associates%20of%20Chaitanya%20Baghel%20were%20among%20the%20locations%20that%20were%20raided%20in%20the%20connection%20with%20the%20money%20laundering%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20is%20linked%20to%20an%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20that%20the%20central%20agency%20believes%20had%20led%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20loss%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer.%20They%20say%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20liquor%20syndicate%20had%20siphoned%20around%20Rs%202%2C161%20crore%20through%20various%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaitanya%20Baghel%20had%20received%20proceeds%20generated%20from%20this%20alleged%20scam%2C%20according%20to%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20investigation%20so%20far%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20liquor%20syndicate%20operated%20between%202019%20and%202022%2C%20which%20generated%20a%20large%20amount%20in%20the%20form%20of%20illegal%20commissions%20through%20multiple%20ways.%20One%20of%20the%20ways%20was%20to%20collect%20bribes%20from%20the%20distillers%20per%20liquor%20'case'%20procured%20by%20the%20state%20liquor%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20scam%20also%20covered%20the%20sale%20of%20country%20liquor%20from%20state-run%20shops%2C%20which%20remained%20entirely%20unaccounted.%20The%20ED%20believes%20that%20not%20a%20single%20rupee%20had%20reached%20the%20state%20exchequer%2C%20and%20all%20the%20money%20was%20pocketed%20by%20the%20syndicate%20suspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistillers%20also%20had%20to%20pay%20a%20bribe%20that%20allowed%20them%20to%20run%20a%20liquor%20cartel%20with%20fixed%20market%20share%2C%20according%20to%20ED.%20Commissions%20were%20also%20charged%20in%20the%20foreign%20liquor%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741585920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F3pks64u8_bhupesh-baghel_625x300_05_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fin