pUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Cuts%20Gaza%20Electricity%20Ahead%20Of%20New%20Talks%2C%20Hamas%20Flags%20%26quot%3BBlackmail%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20ordered%20an%20immediate%20halt%20to%20Gaza's%20electricity%20supply%20Sunday%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20pressure%20Hamas%20into%20releasing%20hostages%2C%20even%20as%20it%20prepared%20for%20fresh%20talks%20on%20the%20future%20of%20its%20truce%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20decision%20comes%20a%20week%20after%20it%20blocked%20all%20aid%20supplies%20to%20the%20war-battered%20territory%2C%20a%20move%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20the%20war%20when%20Israel%20announced%20a%20%26quot%3Bsiege%26quot%3B%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20described%20the%20electricity%20cut%20as%20%26quot%3Bblackmail%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20term%20it%20had%20also%20used%20after%20Israel%20blocked%20the%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truce's%20initial%20phase%20ended%20on%20March%201%20and%20both%20sides%20have%20refrained%20from%20returning%20to%20all-out%20war%2C%20despite%20sporadic%20violence%20including%20an%20air%20strike%20Sunday%20that%20Israel%20said%20targeted%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20start%20to%20negotiations%20on%20the%20ceasefire's%20second%20phase%2C%20aiming%20to%20end%20the%20war%20permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20says%20it%20prefers%20extending%20phase%20one%20until%20mid-April%2C%20and%20halted%20aid%20to%20Gaza%20over%20the%20impasse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20it%20ordered%20a%20cut%20in%20the%20electricity%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20just%20signed%20the%20order%20to%20stop%20supplying%20electricity%20immediately%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%26quot%3B%20Energy%20Minister%20Eli%20Cohen%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20use%20all%20the%20tools%20at%20our%20disposal%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20hostages%20and%20ensure%20that%20Hamas%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20Gaza%20the%20day%20after%26quot%3B%20the%20war%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIzzat%20al-Rishq%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Hamas's%20political%20bureau%2C%20described%20Israel's%20move%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20pressure%20our%20people%20and%20their%20resistance%20through%20cheap%20and%20unacceptable%20blackmail%20tactics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20days%20after%20the%20war%20erupted%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%20after%20Hamas's%20attack%2C%20Israel%20cut%20electricity%20to%20Gaza%2C%20only%20restoring%20it%20in%20mid-2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sole%20power%20line%20between%20Israel%20and%20Gaza%20supplies%20the%20main%20desalination%20plant%2C%20and%20Gazans%20mainly%20rely%20now%20on%20solar%20panels%20and%20fuel-powered%20generators%20to%20produce%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20live%20in%20tents%2C%20with%20night-time%20temperatures%20now%20forecast%20around%2012%20degrees%20Celsius%20(54%20Fahrenheit).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESituation%20'dire'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20representatives%20met%20Egyptian%20mediators%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20emphasising%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20resume%20aid%20deliveries%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20restrictions%20or%20conditions%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20Hamas%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20call%20on%20mediators%20in%20Egypt%20and%20Qatar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20guarantors%20in%20the%20US%20administration%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20(Israeli)%20occupation%20complies%20with%20the%20agreement...%20and%20proceeds%20with%20the%20second%20phase%20according%20to%20the%20agreed-upon%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20spokesman%20Hazem%20Qassem%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20key%20demands%20for%20the%20second%20phase%20include%20a%20hostage-prisoner%20exchange%2C%20Israel's%20complete%20withdrawal%20from%20Gaza%2C%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire%2C%20border%20crossings%20reopening%20and%20lifting%20the%20blockade%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20United%20States%20president%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20also%20outlined%20a%20second%20phase%20involving%20the%20release%20of%20remaining%20living%20hostages%2C%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20Israeli%20forces%20left%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20establishment%20of%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20mediators%2C%20another%20Hamas%20spokesman%2C%20Abdel%20Latif%20al-Qanoua%2C%20said%20indicators%20were%20so%20far%20%26quot%3Bpositive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%20said%20it%20would%20send%20delegates%20to%20Doha%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truce%20largely%20halted%20more%20than%2015%20months%20of%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20virtually%20the%20entire%20population%20was%20displaced%20by%20Israel's%20relentless%20military%20campaign%20in%20response%20to%20the%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six-week%20first%20phase%20led%20to%20the%20exchange%20of%2025%20living%20Israeli%20hostages%20and%20eight%20bodies%20for%20the%20release%20of%20about%201%2C800%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20held%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20allowed%20in%20much-needed%20food%2C%20shelter%20and%20medical%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Israel%20cut%20off%20the%20aid%20flow%2C%20UN%20rights%20experts%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20%26quot%3Bweaponising%20starvation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20UN%20distribution%20of%20flour%20in%20Jabalia%2C%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20Abu%20Mahmoud%20Salman%2C%2056%2C%20said%20that%20with%20the%20territory%20now%20closed%20off%20from%20fresh%20supplies%2C%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bfears%20of%20renewed%20famine%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20the%20situation%20remains%20dire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFears%20for%20hostages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C