idents%20arrived%20in%201996%20after%20winning%20a%20housing%20lottery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20about%2011%2C000%20Central%20Florida%20residents%20call%20Celebration%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Walt%20Disney%20Company%20had%20an%20ambitious%20plan%20in%20the%201990s%3A%20build%20a%20picture-perfect%20community%20brimming%20with%20the%20charm%20and%20feel%20of%20America's%20small%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20the%20company%20had%20primarily%20focused%20on%20attractions%20and%20entertainment%20projects%20when%20it%20developed%20Celebration%2C%20which%20is%20a%20residential%20community%20just%2015%20minutes%20from%20Walt%20Disney%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20visiting%20family%20in%20Orlando%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20drive%20to%20Celebration%20to%20explore%20the%20community%2029%20years%20after%20the%20first%20families%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20also%20spoke%20with%20Joe%20Davison%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20postmen%20in%20Celebration.%20He%20began%20working%20at%20its%20post%20office%20in%201996%20and%20retired%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20trade%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20by%20far%20the%20best%2013%20years%20of%20work%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20spoke%20with%20Celebration%20HOA%20President%20Don%20McDonald%2C%20who%20has%20lived%20there%20with%20his%20family%20since%20the%20mid-1990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20few%20years%20it%20was%20very%20tight%20knit%2C%26quot%3B%20McDonald%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20only%20a%20hundred%20and%20some%20odd%20houses.%20We%20knew%20everybody%20and%20the%20kids%20knew%20everybody%2C%20and%20we%20felt%20relatively%20safe%20letting%20the%20kids%20run%20free%20and%20free%20range.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDisney%20broke%20ground%20in%201994.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224204%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Homes%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20under%20construction%20in%201996.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad04b66630eb10385c6ff0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222820%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelebration%20under%20construction%20in%20the%20mid-1990s.%3Cp%3Emark%20peterson%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Celebration%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20The%20Walt%20Disney%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20developed%20the%20community%20with%20the%20help%20of%20several%20architects%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-stern-why-architects-should-draw-no-computer-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20A.M.%20Stern%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Stern's%20firm%20helped%20create%20the%20master%20plan%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20build%20a%20picturesque%20landscape%20endowed%20with%20small-town%20charm%20and%20Southern%20flair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20emphasis%20on%20tree-lined%20streets%2C%20parks%2C%20and%20civic%20buildings%20will%20create%20a%20strong%20public%20realm%2C%20an%20essential%20ingredient%20to%20any%20real%20town%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ramsa.com%2Fprojects%2Fproject%2Fcelebration%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommunity%20is%20the%20main%20focus%20in%20Celebration%2C%20so%20the%20architects%20created%20their%20designs%20to%20encourage%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGarages%20are%20located%20on%20alleys%2C%20opening%20the%20streets%20to%20views%20of%20houses%20rather%20than%20garage%20doors%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20allowing%20for%20narrower%20lots%20which%20decrease%20walking%20distances%20and%20enhance%20the%20sense%20of%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%20on%20a%20balmy%20Saturday%2C%20the%20community%20appeared%20especially%20lively.%20A%20group%20of%20children%20performed%20a%20choreographed%20dance%20in%20a