0but%20we%20weren't%20really%20that%20busy%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20the%20post%20office%20during%20Celebration's%20early%20years%20allowed%20Davison%20to%20meet%20many%20of%20the%20new%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20point%20in%20time%2C%20the%20post%20office%20was%20pretty%20slow%2C%20so%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20coming%20in%20were%20residents%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20atmosphere%20among%20residents%20in%20Celebration%20was%20welcoming%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20different%20from%20his%20previous%20post%20office%20job%20in%20South%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20them%20would%20let%20you%20know%20you%20didn't%20live%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said%20about%20Miami.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Celebration%2C%20nobody%20ever%20treated%20me%20like%20an%20outsider%2C%20which%20is%20nice%20in%20that%20respect.%20You%20felt%20like%20part%20of%20the%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%202%2C700%20people%20called%20Celebration%20home%20by%202000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20census%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20modern%20Celebration%20homes%20cost%20millions.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Homes%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%20February%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad06b47bb3f854015cb2c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EResidential%20homes%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%202025.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECelebration%20has%20grown%20quite%20a%20bit%20since%20the%20first%20residents%20arrived%20in%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20neighborhood%20%E2%80%94%20or%20village%20%E2%80%94%20expansions%20were%20completed%20from%202000%20to%202003.%20The%20most%20recent%20expansion%20happened%20in%202021%20with%20Island%20Village%2C%20which%20is%20nestled%20into%20t