Starbucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20walking%20through%20the%20town%20center%2C%20all%20I%20could%20think%20about%20was%20how%20it%20perfectly%20encapsulated%20the%20nostalgia%20of%20small%20American%20towns.%20Couples%20enjoyed%20fudge%20treats%20%E2%80%94%20courtesy%20of%20Kilwins%20Chocolate%20and%20Ice%20Cream%20Shop%20%E2%80%94%20while%20friends%20darted%20in%20and%20out%20of%20boutique%20shops.%20The%20streets%20were%20lined%20with%20pastel-colored%20buildings%2C%20including%20restaurants%20that%20overlooked%20Lake%20Rianhard%20and%20Lakeside%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Celebration%20seems%20almost%20artificially%20perfect%2C%20McDonald%20said%20his%20community%20is%20very%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20'The%20Stepford%20Wives'%20or%20'The%20Truman%20Show%2C'%26quot%3B%20McDonald%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20artificial%20birds%20in%20the%20tree.%20Every%20one%20of%20those%20birds%20is%20a%20real%20bird.%20They%20wake%20me%20up%20in%20the%20morning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20shops%20are%20still%20in%20Celebration%20decades%20later.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223021%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Market%20Street%20Gallery%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%20February%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad0f506630eb10385c7355%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarket%20Street%20Gallery%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%202025.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPhotographs%20from%20the%201990s%20offer%20a%20glimpse%20into%20Celebration's%20early%20years%2C%20when%20shops%20and%20stores%20lined%20Market%20Street%2C%20including%20Market%20Street%20Gallery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ventured%20inside%2C%20where%20they%20sold%20everything%20from%20sparkling%20Christmas%20ornaments%20to%20home%20decor.%20Items%20based%20on%20Disney%20characters%20were%20displayed%20around%20the%20shop.%20A%20website%20for%20Celebration's%20Town%20Center%20said%20the%20shop%20acquired%20new%20owners%20in%202019.%20It's%20family-owned%20and%20operated%20by%20Celebration%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavison%20said%20retailers%20settled%20into%20Celebration%2C%20but%20some%20struggled%20to%20remain%20in%20business%20due%20to%20rent%20prices%20and%20what%20he%20considered%20a%20lack%20of%20publicity%20from%20Disney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelebration%20is%20only%20a%2015-minute%20drive%20from%20Magic%20Kingdom%2C%20meaning%20it's%20part%20of%20a%20competitive%20tourism%20market%20where%20retailers%20are%20trying%20to%20attract%20tourists%20and%20locals%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBusinesses%20didn't%20stay%20very%20long%20because%20they%20weren't%20making%20it%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald%2C%20who%20used%20to%20own%20antique%20map%20store%20in%20Celebration%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20compete.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Celebration%20ever%20got%20a%20makeover%2C%20McDonald%20said%20building%20the%20downtown%20closer%20to%20U.S.%20Highway%20192%20could%20benefit%20the%20retailers%20because%20they'd%20be%20closer%20to%20the%20broader%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECelebration's%20iconic%20movie%20theatre%20is%20now%20defunct.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Old%20movie%20theater%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%20February%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad11d26630eb10385c7449%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20AMC%20Theatre%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%20February%202025.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDavison%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-world-mystery-of-movie-theater-in-celebration-florida-being-closed-2018-3%5C%22%20targe